    "long_instructions": "#Web App Wireframe\r\n\r\n1. Choose one of the following ideas for your website:\r\n    - Local Food Vendor Website\r\n    - School Club Website\r\n    - Your own idea!\r\n2. Chat with the AI about how to design two different pages of your website. For example, Home, Menu, Contact, About Me.\r\n3. Ask about boxes, images, and structure.\r\n4. Share your ideas, upload images, and get feedback or refinements from the AI.\r\n5. Record your wireframe ideas in your activity guide. ",
